WEBVTT

40:15.870 --> 40:17.390 line:80%
We have waited for 2 hours.

40:17.600 --> 40:19.000 line:80%
We won't wait any longer.

40:19.030 --> 40:21.090 line:80%
Since the plaintiff has not arrived,

40:21.280 --> 40:23.030 line:80%
I now pronounce

40:23.200 --> 40:25.060 line:80%
that the defendant wins the case!

40:25.720 --> 40:27.080 line:80%
My Lord!
